This paper discusses the production gains and productivity of open source software, which falls under the category of computational science (cs.CY). The paper also discusses collective intelligence and team performance, which are topics related to social and information sciences (cs.SI), software engineering (cs.SE), and systems and control (cs.SD). Finally, the paper discusses the management of teams, which falls under the category of human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
